She's lived in the Africa,
the Soviet Union and in the US

00:06:54.360 --> 00:07:02.480
as she brings all these locations
into bearing as she reflects

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:05.930
on a wide range of topics.

00:07:05.930 --> 00:07:15.390
And then we have Moses Ochonu who
