00:23:37.700 --> 00:23:43.310
Well there's a disconnect between
job satisfaction and education.

00:23:43.310 --> 00:23:48.890
And almost 40% say that
they are not very happy.

00:23:48.890 --> 00:23:51.520
And the reason has
to do with the fact

00:23:51.520 --> 00:23:55.570
