some countries in South Africa

00:27:29.220 --> 00:27:35.410
and Kenya are beginning to
revise many of these regulations.

00:27:35.410 --> 00:27:38.730
But for most of Africa,
the women don't want

00:27:38.730 --> 00:27:44.560
to go back, which is very clear.

00:27:44.560 --> 00:27:49.430
When we collect all these
