to discount stories of successful,

00:52:57.840 --> 00:53:00.720
talented African migrants
to America.

00:53:00.720 --> 00:53:04.940
It also makes it easy for them to
believe that Africans are desperate

00:53:04.940 --> 00:53:08.550
to escape the horrors of their
homelands to come to America.

00:53:08.550 --> 00:53:12.050
