self-assuring because it works

00:53:12.050 --> 00:53:15.700 position:56%
to reaffirm the belief that
America is a generous, compassionate

00:53:15.700 --> 00:53:17.300
and humanitarian country.

00:53:17.300 --> 00:53:21.010
One that is receptive
to African refugees.

00:53:21.010 --> 00:53:24.360
The template seems clear and
it's summed by its simplicity.

00:53:24.360 --> 00:53:30.580
Africa is a land that
perennially produces refugees

00:53:30.580 --> 00:53:33.470
and America is a country
that motivated

00:53:33.470 --> 00:53:36.880
