person of African descent.

01:03:39.250 --> 01:03:43.340
He went on to empathically
state that the bill was "unjust,

01:03:43.340 --> 01:03:45.940
unreasonable and unnecessary."

01:03:45.940 --> 01:03:49.940
It is unnecessary, he proclaimed,
because only a few thousand people

01:03:49.940 --> 01:03:52.950
of African descent enter
this country annually.

01:03:52.950 --> 01:03:56.580 position:56%
