come are mainly from the West Indies

01:03:56.580 --> 01:04:00.350
and almost none from
the continent of Africa.

01:04:00.350 --> 01:04:03.960
Washington went on to cite
the 1910 census pointing

01:04:03.960 --> 01:04:09.370
out that only 40,319 blacks in the
United States were foreign born,

01:04:09.370 --> 01:04:13.280
and only 473 of those
were from Africa.

01:04:13.280 --> 01:04:17.880 position:56%
He further noted that the
immigration bill puts an unnecessary

01:04:17.880 --> 01:04:22.980
