American society.

01:05:36.170 --> 01:05:39.220
Although the large African presence
in the United States resulted

01:05:39.220 --> 01:05:42.230
from the involuntary migration
of men and women and slave

01:05:42.230 --> 01:05:45.340
on the continent since
the 17th century,

01:05:45.340 --> 01:05:49.140
