Africans from the continent came

01:05:49.140 --> 01:05:51.200
to the United States
in small numbers.

01:05:51.200 --> 01:05:54.450
And the most studied group
of African immigrants

01:05:54.450 --> 01:05:57.330
in that period are
probably the Cape Verdeans.

01:05:57.330 --> 01:05:59.840
Most people know about that group.

01:05:59.840 --> 01:06:03.180
Throughout the late 19th
century, Africans trickled

01:06:03.180 --> 01:06:07.710
