their native-born American--

01:06:35.220 --> 01:06:37.330
black American counterparts.

01:06:37.330 --> 01:06:40.530
These interactions were often
guided by prevailing stereotypes

01:06:40.530 --> 01:06:44.440
of Africa held by Americans
in general.

01:06:44.440 --> 01:06:47.440
The predominant view held by
most Americans was, of course,

01:06:47.440 --> 01:06:50.000
