01:06:50.000 --> 01:06:54.050
Largely negative portraying the
continent as savage, barbaric,

01:06:54.050 --> 01:06:57.790
needing uplift from
those more civilized.

01:06:57.790 --> 01:07:01.020
Because of the difficulties
adjusting to the African climate,

01:07:01.020 --> 01:07:03.570
