black churches

01:07:03.570 --> 01:07:07.480
and black missionaries start to
train Native Africans to serve

01:07:07.480 --> 01:07:09.170
as missionaries in
their own native land,

01:07:09.170 --> 01:07:12.300
so black missionaries
would encourage Africans

01:07:12.300 --> 01:07:16.030
to come to the United States.

01:07:16.030 --> 01:07:19.360
And these students came to the
United States a lot of times

01:07:19.360 --> 01:07:22.710
under the auspices of these
African-American missions.

01:07:22.710 --> 01:07:25.680
They offered African-Americans
the first opportunities to see

01:07:25.680 --> 01:07:27.110
