01:29:52.320 --> 01:29:55.170
as the land of the black.

01:29:55.170 --> 01:30:00.560
We rejected the European
framing of it.

01:30:00.560 --> 01:30:04.360
And Washington, DC takes
the earlier European framing

01:30:04.360 --> 01:30:09.130
in which they lumped part of
North Africa with the Middle East

01:30:09.130 --> 01:30:14.270
and it is Du Bois in that
