01:30:14.270 --> 01:30:19.110
we are going to frame-- We are
now going to disconnect Africa

01:30:19.110 --> 01:30:21.770
from Egypt from North Africa."

01:30:21.770 --> 01:30:24.460
And that is what that
state in Africa itself

01:30:24.460 --> 01:30:30.610
and the way in which we teach.

01:30:30.610 --> 01:30:37.040
And you'll find when we go into the
academic understanding of Africa--

01:30:37.040 --> 01:30:38.340
&gt;&gt; The restroom is this way, yes.

