01:30:54.500 --> 01:30:58.620
It is true that contemporary
immigrants are not connected

01:30:58.620 --> 01:31:01.160
with the civil rights movement.

01:31:01.160 --> 01:31:04.940
Many of them are beneficiaries
of the struggles

01:31:04.940 --> 01:31:11.160
but they did not contribute to
the struggle and it shapes some

01:31:11.160 --> 01:31:14.070
