01:32:16.030 --> 01:32:19.330
But now, officially,
Africa has six regions

01:32:19.330 --> 01:32:24.070
in which they now include
the African diaspora

01:32:24.070 --> 01:32:26.660
as an official sixth region.

01:32:26.660 --> 01:32:34.090
And how this will be connected to
textbook writings, on politics,

01:32:34.090 --> 01:32:38.820
on policies are things we
have to pay attention to.

