stealing from the cookie jar.

01:49:46.750 --> 01:49:52.510
Wainaina's writing speaks of the
new Africa in a new global style

01:49:52.510 --> 01:49:56.000
that captures the still
existent old world of politics

01:49:56.000 --> 01:49:59.310
with the old autocracies
emerging in the icy waters

01:49:59.310 --> 01:50:02.070 position:56%
of new journalistic instant texting.

01:50:02.070 --> 01:50:05.650
He's created a new story
not because of the scandal

01:50:05.650 --> 01:50:10.360
