pessimistic plucking but because

01:50:10.360 --> 01:50:13.290
of how we now desuture
ourselves from what we thought

01:50:13.290 --> 01:50:15.020
to be African literature

01:50:15.020 --> 01:50:19.630
and resuture the identification
with the reportage.

